OL,3,CPlanned charity and volunteer sector
OL,4,Ccut 'cruel'
OL,6,FA proposed 64% funding cut to the
OL,7,Fcharity and volunteer sector in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland has been described as
OL,9,F"cruel" and "devastating" by those who
OL,10,Fwork with the most vulnerable in our
OL,11,Fsociety.
OL,13,FThe UK Government fund helps around
OL,14,F11,000 service users here. Hundreds of
OL,15,Fjobs are now at risk, because an end
OL,16,Fof January deadline is looming for a
OL,17,Ffinal decision to be made.
OL,19,FSector workers and service users held
OL,20,Fa demonstration at Stormont on
OL,21,FWednesday.
