OL,3,CPlanned charity and volunteer sector
OL,4,Ccut 'cruel'
OL,6,FCeline McStravick from NICVA said:
OL,7,F"Organisations delivering proven
OL,8,Foutcomes are being pushed to the edge
OL,9,Fwith weeks' notice and no transition,
OL,10,Fwhile being told that responsibility
OL,11,Flies 'elsewhere' or that processes
OL,12,F'take time'.
OL,14,F"We already lag behind the rest of the
OL,15,FUK in access to key programmes. That
OL,16,Fshould alarm anyone who cares about
OL,17,Ffairness, prevention, and value for
OL,18,Fpublic money."
