OL,4,Ccut 'cruel'
OL,6,FThe UK Shared Prosperity Fund will be
OL,7,Freplaced by the Local Growth Fund from
OL,8,FApril, which will mean funding will be
OL,9,Fcut from #25m to #9.2m.
OL,11,F"This is not special pleading - it is
OL,12,Fabout protecting the infrastructure
OL,13,Fthat underpins health, employability,
OL,14,Fand community stability," continued
OL,15,FCeline McStravick.
OL,17,F"If these services fall, the cost will
OL,18,Fsimply reappear elsewhere: in crisis
OL,19,Fresponses, overstretched public
OL,20,Fservices, and lives pushed further
OL,21,Ffrom opportunity."
