OL,6,FThe Stormont Executive is being asked
OL,7,Fto help, with Finance Minister John
OL,8,FO'Dowd now being asked to find a way
OL,9,Fto plug the funding gap with an
OL,10,Falready stretched draft multi-year
OL,11,Fbudget.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,14,FFinance said: "Since taking office,
OL,15,Fthe Finance Minister has repeatedly
OL,16,Fpressed the Westminster Government for
OL,17,Fclarity on Local Growth funding.
